Where I think Pantheon should lean in

Your project already has strong conceptual depth.

I think the next frontier is making it pleasant to traverse.

That means investing in:

* visual maps
* progressive disclosure
* interactive games (Hammer Mole is one example)
* relationship explorers
* timelines
* provenance views
* multiple zoom levels

Not because the ideas need changing, but because navigation is becoming the bottleneck.

